4112", "description": "A free, open-source gold price tracker. Monitor real-time gold prices from multiple sources, set price alerts, and track market trends - all from your device. No accounts, no tracking.\n\nFeatures:\n\nPrice Tracking:\n- Real-time gold price updates from multiple sources\n- Support for various gold types (Antam, Logam Mulia, etc.)\n- Price history with charts and trend analysis\n- Multiple karat support (24K, 22K, 21K, 18K)\n\nAlerts & Notifications:\n- Customizable price alerts for buy/sell targets\n- Push notifications when price thresholds are reached\n- Price change percentage alerts\n\nMarket Data:\n- Buy and sell price display\n- Price spread calculation\n- Daily, weekly, and monthly price change tracking\n- Currency conversion support\n\nUser Interface:\n- Clean and intuitive dashboard\n- Dark theme support\n- Home screen widget for quick price glance\n- Offline last-known price display\n", "issueTracker": "https://github.com/iamutaki/radar-emas/issues", "license": "Unknown", "name": "Radar Emas", "sourceCode": "https://github.com/iamutaki/radar-emas", "summary": "Free, open-source gold price tracker - monitor harga emas real-time", "webSite": "https://iamutaki.github.io/", "added": 1780951528000, "packageName": "dev.cacing69.radar_emas", "lastUpdated": 1780951529000, "localized": {"en-US": {"icon": "icon_cJS6r58Vl5TQQyiXdK638iRtthc84Y0X5Mze0ZpYqK0=.png", "phoneScreenshots": ["01.jpeg", "02.jpeg"]}}}], "packages": {"dev.cacing69.curel": [{"added": 1780951528000, "apkName": "dev.cacing69.curel-x86_64.apk", "hash": "79a127eaad29567dbb79fd02eb07324c012b54d416c45c15d21a2786a59d67f7", "hashType": "sha256", "minSdkVersion": 24, "nativecode": ["x86_64"], "packageName": "dev.cacing69.curel", "sig": "4de904f847a9c4421e0a4af61334925b", "signer": "251b142020e72938df647f22a373b93d9240ba3cbcd232f86772ad9007564a44", "size": 25792599, "targetSdkVersion": 36, "uses-permission": [["android.permission.INTERNET", null], ["dev.cacing69.curel.DYNAMIC_RECEIVE